Package: quick_stats
Type: Package
Title: Quick Summary Statistics for Data Frames
Version: 0.1.1
Authors@R: person("Maddy", "Riddler", email = "mriddler@student.ubc.ca", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides tools for quickly calculating useful summary statistics 
    (such as mean, median, mode, standard deviation, and range) for all numeric 
    variables in a data frame. The package includes functions for handling 
    missing values and generating comprehensive statistical summaries, 
    with options for customizing output formats.
License: MIT
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Imports:
    dplyr,
    tidyr,
    rlang,
    magrittr
RoxygenNote: 7.3.2
